Lunarpine sniffed around as he fired at Ares, he caught Shadow Wings 
scent again, along with the strong scent of fluid, she was hurt but 
still moving. he also knew someone was following her. probably the 
same one who wounded her to begin with. He knew he had to dispose of 
this target fast and go find wing. 

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, logomorph@h... wrote:
> ::Shadow Wing::
> 
> She felt her wing and desided to try to transform.  She was 
> successful.  She spread her wings and flew up just as she was about 
> to reach the front of the Ark.  It was trmediously painful and the 
> pain screamed through her body.  She up and landed in a tree next 
to 
> the Ark. She looked down and saw Killer.  She was feeling her owl 
> instincts trying to take over.  But the damage to her body was 
> getting to her.  She just sat on the branch and tried to regain her 
> breath.
